summary: So I saw Endgame Last night
body:
So I saw Endgame Last night

I think it was better than Infinity War (I think a lot of people would say it was better than infinity war) but I genuinely mean it. I was on a roller coaster of emotions, in the end I was in a bittersweet kind of trance. I think they ended it better than I could have ever imagined, but my heart still aches.

I’m trying not give away spoilers so I’ll keep this short. When you go to see this movie, bring your friends, bring some tissues because goodness knows you’ll need them (unless your a psychopath like me and can’t cry). Squeeze your friends’ hands, give them a hug afterwards, I think we all needed a hug after.

Just remember, this may be the end, but it’s the beginning of so many new heroes and stories.
